# UI Components

This project uses [shadcn/ui](mdc:https:/ui.shadcn.com) - a collection of reusable components built with [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com) and [Radix UI](mdc:https:/www.radix-ui.com).

## UI Components
- [button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx) - Button component
- [card.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/card.tsx) - Card component
- [form.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/form.tsx) - Form components
- [input.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/input.tsx) - Input component
- [label.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/label.tsx) - Label component
- [select.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/select.tsx) - Select component
- [sonner.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/sonner.tsx) - Toast notifications
- [tabs.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/tabs.tsx) - Tabs component
- [textarea.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/textarea.tsx) - Textarea component

## Component Patterns
- Components use class-variance-authority (cva) for variant management
- Tailwind is used for styling through shadcn/ui's component design
- Components are built on top of Radix UI primitives for accessibility
- Add new components using `pnpm dlx shadcn-ui@latest add [component-name]`